{
  "stem": "9503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the things that my mother afterwards said was her pride-- that she got me through the camp with my hair.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, she put big-- that-- that was her chance to show her mothering.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I never had lice, head lice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] You know, people do the best they can, and my mother did the best that she could.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to her, this was very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember one shower.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Red Cross came to inspect the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the orphanage was going to be held up as a-- an example of how good the Germans were to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we were moved to a house, and we were given rooms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And instead of three flights-- three-deckers, there were two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were-- there were no more, I think, than six in a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was an actual shower, and we all took a turn and had a shower there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember icky soap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the Red Cross Commission and Germans inspected this house, and I remember sitting on my bunk and just looking down.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I did-- I figured if I don't see them, they don't see me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know how children sometimes think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And even at that age, I remember the black boots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when the Red Cross Commission left the camp, we were moved back and things went back to normal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "During that time period that the Red Cross Commission was there we got different food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They also [SIGHS] said that we had the chance to purchase things.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
